    "description": "UMC Electronics Co., Ltd. provides electronic manufacturing services in Japan. The company offers in-vehicle equipment, including electrical systems for electric vehicles, starting and power generation equipment, exterior systems, speedometers, in-vehicle environmental control equipment, and security devices, as well as automotive electronic devices comprising powertrain, control, and drive systems. It also provides industrial equipment, such as inverters, servo motors, electronic boards for IC testers, smart meters, small inverters, servers, storage, and semiconductor test equipment; office equipment that include circuit boards for printers and copiers; electronic boards for air conditioners; and module products for game machines, and audio and image control boards. In addition, the company offers temporary staffing and manufacturing contract services. UMC Electronics Co., Ltd. was incorporated in 1968 and is headquartered in Ageo, Japan."
